[{"data":1,"prerenderedAt":1388},["ShallowReactive",2],{"header-locale:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231013\u002F3280561145\u002F":3,"page:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231013\u002F3280561145\u002F":4,"alt:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231013\u002F3280561145\u002F":3,"prev-next:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231013\u002F3280561145\u002F":1363,"related:\u002Fnodejs\u002F20231013\u002F3280561145\u002F":1372},"\u002Fen\u002Fnodejs\u002F2023\u002F10\u002F13\u002Fday-29-about-jwt-authentication\u002F",{"id":5,"title":6,"abbrlink":7,"altUrl":3,"body":8,"category":1347,"date":1348,"description":25,"extension":1349,"lang":1350,"meta":1351,"navigation":685,"path":1352,"readingMinutes":1353,"seo":1354,"standalone":1355,"stem":1356,"tags":1357,"tldr":1360,"updated":1348,"url":1361,"__hash__":1362},"content\u002F《Node.js 不負責系列：把前端人員當作後端來用，就算是前端也能嘗試寫的後端～原來 Node.js 可以做這麼多事～》\u002FDay29-關於-JWT-驗證.md","Day29-關於 JWT 驗證","3280561145",{"type":9,"value":10,"toc":1336},"minimark",[11,19,23,26,29,32,35,38,48,52,63,66,94,111,114,123,126,148,152,155,171,176,179,187,190,198,202,205,274,277,285,288,299,302,305,308,331,334,384,391,395,398,444,447,483,486,518,521,555,558,561,564,572,581,587,590,593,596,973,976,982,985,988,991,995,1002,1020,1026,1121,1127,1138,1144,1147,1199,1206,1310,1313,1329,1332],[12,13,14],"p",{},[15,16],"img",{"alt":17,"src":18},"關於 JWT 驗證","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fisray_notarray_web_Certification_87b4aacf-552a-40c1-8cb8-9fa5dca7d52d.png",[20,21,22],"h2",{"id":22},"前言",[12,24,25],{},"接下來這一篇將會來介紹 JWT 的驗證，畢竟前面一直都沒提到，可是實戰上來講卻是非常重要的一環哩。",[20,27,28],{"id":28},"身份認證",[12,30,31],{},"為什麼要身份認證呢？前面的許多章節中，其實我們都沒有做身份認證的機制，舉凡 API、Discord、Chrome Extension 等等，都沒有做身份認證，那麼為什麼要做身份認證呢？",[12,33,34],{},"我們所開發的東西有些功能是僅限於特定的人才能使用，例如：管理員、VIP 等等，這時候我們就需要一個機制來做身份認證，那麼這時候就會提到 JWT（JSON Web Token）了。",[12,36,37],{},"而現今主流開發比較常見於前後端分離的架構，不再是傳統的 SSR（Server Side Rendering）的架構，前端大多都是透過後端所提供的 API 來取得資料，而這個取資料的過程就必須要被認證。",[39,40,41],"blockquote",{},[12,42,43,47],{},[44,45,46],"strong",{},"Note","\n早期開發時，使用者登入後，後端會將使用者的 UID 儲存在伺服器的記憶體中（Session），但因為現今主流開發事前後端分離的架構，因此這種方式已經不適用了，因此就有了 JWT。",[20,49,51],{"id":50},"json-web-token-是什麼","JSON Web Token 是什麼？",[12,53,54,55,62],{},"剛才有提到 JWT 的全名是 JSON Web Token，是一個廣泛被使用來驗證與授權的標準，尤其是在網頁開發上很常被使用，而且也是一個開放的標準（",[56,57,61],"a",{"href":58,"rel":59},"https:\u002F\u002Fdatatracker.ietf.org\u002Fdoc\u002Fhtml\u002Frfc7519",[60],"nofollow","RFC 7519","）。",[12,64,65],{},"基本上 JWT 的結構分為三個部分：",[67,68,69,78,86],"ul",{},[70,71,72,73],"li",{},"HEADER（標頭）：ALGORITHM & TOKEN TYPE\n",[67,74,75],{},[70,76,77],{},"用來說明這一組 Token 是用什麼演算法加密的，以及 Token 的類型",[70,79,80,81],{},"PAYLOAD（負載）：DATA\n",[67,82,83],{},[70,84,85],{},"主要是用來存放一些資料，例如使用者的 ID、名字等等",[70,87,88,89],{},"VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名）\n",[67,90,91],{},[70,92,93],{},"這一部分是用來驗證 Token 是否為正確的 Token",[95,96,101],"pre",{"className":97,"code":98,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},"language-txt shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c\n","txt","",[102,103,104],"code",{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,106,109],"span",{"class":107,"line":108},"line",1,[105,110,98],{},[12,112,113],{},"很難看出其差異吧？如果我依據上面的結構來拆解的話，就會變成這樣：",[95,115,117],{"className":97,"code":116,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},"HEADER.PAYLOAD.VERIFY SIGNATURE\n",[102,118,119],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,120,121],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,122,116],{},[12,124,125],{},"搭配上方的 JWT 範例，就會變成這樣：",[95,127,129],{"className":97,"code":128,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.  # HEADER（標頭）\neyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ. # PAYLOAD（負載）\nSflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c # VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名）\n",[102,130,131,136,142],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,132,133],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,134,135],{},"eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.  # HEADER（標頭）\n",[105,137,139],{"class":107,"line":138},2,[105,140,141],{},"eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ. # PAYLOAD（負載）\n",[105,143,145],{"class":107,"line":144},3,[105,146,147],{},"SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c # VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名）\n",[20,149,151],{"id":150},"jwt-原理","JWT 原理",[12,153,154],{},"那麼 JWT 是如何實作出來的呢？剛才有提到 JWT 的結構分為三個部分，其實比較核心的部分是 PAYLOAD（負載）與 VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名），但我們還是針對 JWT 三個部分來做介紹，而這邊示範的範例會是前面所講的 JWT Token 範例：",[95,156,157],{"className":97,"code":128,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},[102,158,159,163,167],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,160,161],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,162,135],{},[105,164,165],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,166,141],{},[105,168,169],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,170,147],{},[172,173,175],"h3",{"id":174},"header標頭","HEADER（標頭）",[12,177,178],{},"HEADER 主要組合會是兩個部分：",[67,180,181,184],{},[70,182,183],{},"alg（Algorithm）：加密演算法",[70,185,186],{},"typ（Type）：Token 類型",[12,188,189],{},"而這兩個部分會被編碼成 Base64 字串，例如：",[95,191,192],{"className":97,"code":135,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},[102,193,194],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,195,196],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,197,135],{},[172,199,201],{"id":200},"payload負載","PAYLOAD（負載）",[12,203,204],{},"PAYLOAD（負載）的部分，其實就是一個 JSON 物件，例如：",[95,206,210],{"className":207,"code":208,"language":209,"meta":100,"style":100},"language-json shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","{\n  \"username\": \"Ray\", \u002F\u002F 使用者名稱\n  \"email\": \"example.com\", \u002F\u002F 使用者信箱\n  \"iat\": 1516239022 \u002F\u002F 簽發（Issued At）時間\n}\n","json",[102,211,212,218,238,253,268],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,213,214],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,215,217],{"class":216},"sMAXC","{\n",[105,219,220,224,227,231,234],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,221,223],{"class":222},"sKpQp","  \"username\"",[105,225,226],{"class":216},": ",[105,228,230],{"class":229},"sTRMh","\"Ray\"",[105,232,233],{"class":216},", ",[105,235,237],{"class":236},"sQrFR","\u002F\u002F 使用者名稱\n",[105,239,240,243,245,248,250],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,241,242],{"class":222},"  \"email\"",[105,244,226],{"class":216},[105,246,247],{"class":229},"\"example.com\"",[105,249,233],{"class":216},[105,251,252],{"class":236},"\u002F\u002F 使用者信箱\n",[105,254,256,259,261,265],{"class":107,"line":255},4,[105,257,258],{"class":222},"  \"iat\"",[105,260,226],{"class":216},[105,262,264],{"class":263},"sCcAr","1516239022",[105,266,267],{"class":236}," \u002F\u002F 簽發（Issued At）時間\n",[105,269,271],{"class":107,"line":270},5,[105,272,273],{"class":216},"}\n",[12,275,276],{},"而這個 JSON 物件會被編碼成 Base64 字串，例如：",[95,278,279],{"className":97,"code":141,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},[102,280,281],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,282,283],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,284,141],{},[12,286,287],{},"感覺 PAYLOAD 滿單純的吧？但實際上它是由三個部分組成的，分別是：",[67,289,290,293,296],{},[70,291,292],{},"Registered Claim（註冊聲明）",[70,294,295],{},"Public Claim（公開聲明）",[70,297,298],{},"Private Claim（私有聲明）",[12,300,301],{},"而這三個部分都是選填的，但實戰上來講，通常都會使用 Public Claim（公開聲明）來存放一些資料，例如：使用者的 ID、名字等等。",[12,303,304],{},"比較常見的設定會是 Registered Claim 中的 iat（Issued At）與 exp（Expiration Time），而這兩個屬性可以用來驗證 Token 是否過期等。",[12,306,307],{},"當然，Registered Claim 中還有很多屬性，例如：",[67,309,310,313,316,319,322,325,328],{},[70,311,312],{},"iss（Issuer）：發行者",[70,314,315],{},"sub（Subject）：主體",[70,317,318],{},"aud（Audience）：對象",[70,320,321],{},"exp（Expiration Time）：過期時間",[70,323,324],{},"nbf（Not Before）：生效時間",[70,326,327],{},"iat（Issued At）：簽發時間",[70,329,330],{},"jti（JWT ID）：JWT ID",[12,332,333],{},"因此以上面前面的 JSON 物件來說，就會變成這樣：",[95,335,337],{"className":207,"code":336,"language":209,"meta":100,"style":100},"{\n  \"username\": \"Ray\", \u002F\u002F 使用者名稱 => Public Claim（公開聲明）\n  \"email\": \"example.com\", \u002F\u002F 使用者信箱 => Public Claim（公開聲明）\n  \"iat\": 1516239022 \u002F\u002F 簽發（Issued At）時間 => Registered Claim（註冊聲明）\n}\n",[102,338,339,343,356,369,380],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,340,341],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,342,217],{"class":216},[105,344,345,347,349,351,353],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,346,223],{"class":222},[105,348,226],{"class":216},[105,350,230],{"class":229},[105,352,233],{"class":216},[105,354,355],{"class":236},"\u002F\u002F 使用者名稱 => Public Claim（公開聲明）\n",[105,357,358,360,362,364,366],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,359,242],{"class":222},[105,361,226],{"class":216},[105,363,247],{"class":229},[105,365,233],{"class":216},[105,367,368],{"class":236},"\u002F\u002F 使用者信箱 => Public Claim（公開聲明）\n",[105,370,371,373,375,377],{"class":107,"line":255},[105,372,258],{"class":222},[105,374,226],{"class":216},[105,376,264],{"class":263},[105,378,379],{"class":236}," \u002F\u002F 簽發（Issued At）時間 => Registered Claim（註冊聲明）\n",[105,381,382],{"class":107,"line":270},[105,383,273],{"class":216},[39,385,386],{},[12,387,388,390],{},[44,389,46],{},"\n要注意一下 Claim（聲明）的單字只有三個字母，因為 JWT 旨在簡潔與輕量化，因此 Claim（聲明）的單字只有三個字母。",[172,392,394],{"id":393},"verify-signature驗證簽名","VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名）",[12,396,397],{},"VERIFY SIGNATURE（驗證簽名）的部分，其實就是將 PAYLOAD（負載）與 HEADER（標頭）進行編碼，然後再進行加密，例如：",[95,399,403],{"className":400,"code":401,"language":402,"meta":100,"style":100},"language-js shiki shiki-themes github-dark-high-contrast","HMACSHA256(\n  base64UrlEncode(header) + \".\" +\n  base64UrlEncode(payload),\n  secret)\n","js",[102,404,405,414,432,439],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,406,407,411],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,408,410],{"class":409},"sj_SG","HMACSHA256",[105,412,413],{"class":216},"(\n",[105,415,416,419,422,426,429],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,417,418],{"class":409},"  base64UrlEncode",[105,420,421],{"class":216},"(header) ",[105,423,425],{"class":424},"sWyjQ","+",[105,427,428],{"class":229}," \".\"",[105,430,431],{"class":424}," +\n",[105,433,434,436],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,435,418],{"class":409},[105,437,438],{"class":216},"(payload),\n",[105,440,441],{"class":107,"line":255},[105,442,443],{"class":216},"  secret)\n",[12,445,446],{},"那麼問題來了，JWT 是如何知道要用什麼演算法來加密呢？其實就是透過 HEADER（標頭）來取得，例如：",[95,448,450],{"className":207,"code":449,"language":209,"meta":100,"style":100},"{\n  \"alg\": \"HS256\",\n  \"typ\": \"JWT\"\n}\n",[102,451,452,456,469,479],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,453,454],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,455,217],{"class":216},[105,457,458,461,463,466],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,459,460],{"class":222},"  \"alg\"",[105,462,226],{"class":216},[105,464,465],{"class":229},"\"HS256\"",[105,467,468],{"class":216},",\n",[105,470,471,474,476],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,472,473],{"class":222},"  \"typ\"",[105,475,226],{"class":216},[105,477,478],{"class":229},"\"JWT\"\n",[105,480,481],{"class":107,"line":255},[105,482,273],{"class":216},[12,484,485],{},"如果今天是用 PS256 演算法來加密的話，就會變成這樣：",[95,487,489],{"className":207,"code":488,"language":209,"meta":100,"style":100},"{\n  \"alg\": \"PS256\",\n  \"typ\": \"JWT\"\n}\n",[102,490,491,495,506,514],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,492,493],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,494,217],{"class":216},[105,496,497,499,501,504],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,498,460],{"class":222},[105,500,226],{"class":216},[105,502,503],{"class":229},"\"PS256\"",[105,505,468],{"class":216},[105,507,508,510,512],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,509,473],{"class":222},[105,511,226],{"class":216},[105,513,478],{"class":229},[105,515,516],{"class":107,"line":255},[105,517,273],{"class":216},[12,519,520],{},"接著就會將 PAYLOAD（負載）與 HEADER（標頭）進行編碼，然後再進行加密，例如：",[95,522,524],{"className":400,"code":523,"language":402,"meta":100,"style":100},"PS256(\n  base64UrlEncode(header) + \".\" +\n  base64UrlEncode(payload),\n  secret)\n",[102,525,526,533,545,551],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,527,528,531],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,529,530],{"class":409},"PS256",[105,532,413],{"class":216},[105,534,535,537,539,541,543],{"class":107,"line":138},[105,536,418],{"class":409},[105,538,421],{"class":216},[105,540,425],{"class":424},[105,542,428],{"class":229},[105,544,431],{"class":424},[105,546,547,549],{"class":107,"line":144},[105,548,418],{"class":409},[105,550,438],{"class":216},[105,552,553],{"class":107,"line":255},[105,554,443],{"class":216},[12,556,557],{},"而這個加密後的字串也會被編碼成 Base64 字串。",[12,559,560],{},"那 secret 是什麼呢？其實就是一個私鑰，我們在針對 JWT TOken 生成時，會需要使用一組私鑰，而這組私鑰會被用來加密，而當我們要驗證 JWT Token 時，就會需要使用這組私鑰來解密。",[12,562,563],{},"那麼另一個問題來了，我們生成的 JWT Token：",[95,565,566],{"className":97,"code":98,"language":99,"meta":100,"style":100},[102,567,568],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,569,570],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,571,98],{},[12,573,574,575,580],{},"你可以把它丟到 ",[56,576,579],{"href":577,"rel":578},"https:\u002F\u002Fjwt.io\u002F",[60],"jwt.io"," 這個網站上，然後你就會發現它會自動幫你解析，並且告訴你這個 Token 是用什麼演算法加密的，以及 Token 的類型，如下圖：",[12,582,583],{},[15,584],{"alt":585,"src":586},"JWT Token","https:\u002F\u002Fimages.israynotarray.com\u002Fblog\u002Fnodejs\u002Fithelp-nodejs-2023\u002Fjwt_token.png",[12,588,589],{},"好的，問題來了",[12,591,592],{},"「為什麼我們沒有提供私鑰（secret），但是它卻可以解析出來呢？」",[12,594,595],{},"因為 JWT Token 只是透過 Base64 編碼，而並沒有進行加密，因此你是可以自己寫一個 JWT Token 解析器，這邊我也簡單示範寫一個 JWT Token 解析器範例：",[95,597,599],{"className":400,"code":598,"language":402,"meta":100,"style":100},"\u002F\u002F Base64 解碼\nconst Base64decoded = (str) => {\n  str = str.replace(\u002F-\u002Fg, '+').replace(\u002F_\u002Fg, '\u002F');\n\n  \u002F\u002F 如果字串長度不是 4 的倍數，補上 \"=\"\n  while (str.length % 4 !== 0) {\n    str += '=';\n  }\n\n  return window.atob(str);\n}\n\n\u002F\u002F 解析 JWT Token\nconst jwtTokenEncoded = (str) => {\n  if(!str) return console.log('請輸入 JWT Token');\n  const [header, payload, signature] = str.split('.');\n\n  const headerDecoded = JSON.parse(Base64decoded(header));\n  const payloadDecoded = JSON.parse(Base64decoded(payload));\n\n  return {\n    header: headerDecoded,\n    payload: payloadDecoded,\n  }\n}\n\njwtTokenEncoded('eyJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiIsInR5cCI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJzdWIiOiIxMjM0NTY3ODkwIiwibmFtZSI6IkpvaG4gRG9lIiwiaWF0IjoxNTE2MjM5MDIyfQ.SflKxwRJSMeKKF2QT4fwpMeJf36POk6yJV_adQssw5c')\n",[102,600,601,606,633,681,687,692,719,734,740,745,760,765,770,776,796,826,865,870,897,920,925,932,938,944,949,954,959],{"__ignoreMap":100},[105,602,603],{"class":107,"line":108},[105,604,605],{"